## Key Components
- App.jsx: Main application component that renders Header, Navigation, and Carousel
- Header.jsx: Responsive header with "HOLISTIC TECH AGENCY" text, mobile word stacking
- Navigation.jsx: Desktop horizontal nav + mobile burger menu with "E"/"X" toggle
- Carousel.jsx: Image carousel with auto-advance, fade transitions, and dot navigation
- global.css: CSS constants, font faces, color palette, and utility classes
- Header.css: Header-specific styles with responsive font sizing
- Navigation.css: Navigation styles with mobile burger menu positioning
- Carousel.css: Carousel styles with full-width layout and fade transitions

## Key Variables and Methods

### CSS Custom Properties
- **Theme Colors**: --bg-color, --text-color
- **Font Families**: --font-primary (Helvetica Neue), --font-aovel (Aovel Sans Light), --font-lowvetica (Lowvetica)
- **Font Sizes**: --font-size-xs (0.75rem), --font-size-sm (1rem), --font-size-md (1.5rem), --font-size-lg (2rem), --font-size-xl (3rem)
- **Spacing**: --spacing-left-padding (1rem)
- **Opacity**: --opacity-hover (0.7), --opacity-active (1)

### Color Palette
- **Primary**: --color-primary (#923a26 - reddish brown)
- **Secondary**: --color-secondary (#eccd0f - yellow)
- **Tertiary**: --color-tertiary (#dbc8a0 - beige)
- **Accent**: --color-accent (#e07e00 - orange)
- **Inverted Colors**: --color-primary-invert (#6dc5d9), --color-secondary-invert (#1332f0), --color-tertiary-invert (#24375f), --color-accent-invert (#1f81ff)

### Component Methods
- **Header**: Responsive text layout with mobile word stacking, left alignment
- **Navigation**: Desktop horizontal menu + mobile burger menu with "E"/"X" toggle, top-right positioning
- **Carousel**: Auto-advance every 8 seconds, fade transitions, dot navigation, full-width images

### Utility Classes
- **unselectable**: Prevents text selection across all browsers

